  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1319954/" class="title-link">啃的牙嘣！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1319954"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1245093/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1245093-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1245093/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">船长尼摩</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-06"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-06 20:08:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1319954_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本想买《薄伽梵歌》，没看仔细，而买了此书，也许是大牛的作品，但类文言文的翻译，实在让人啃的腮帮子酸。对于初次接触薄伽梵歌的人，此书绝对不是合适的选择。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1319954/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
